1 the total amount that the enrollee is required to pay out of pocket
2 during a contractually agreed upon period of time for health care
3 services that are included under the health benefit plan of the
4 enrollee, and shall not carry over once a new contract or agreement
5 period for the plan begins.
6 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
